<section id="story" class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">
        Our Love Story
      </h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary-500 mx-auto"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-200 to-accent-200 rounded-2xl aspect-square flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center p-8">
            <svg class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto text-white mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.172 5.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L10 6.343l1.172-1.171a4 4 0 115.656 5.656L10 17.657l-6.828-6.829a4 4 0 010-5.656z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-white text-lg font-semibold">First Meeting</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-primary-600 mb-4">
          How We Met
        </h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Our story began on a rainy autumn evening at a cozy coffee shop in downtown Portland. 
          Katie was reading her favorite book, and Clark accidentally spilled his latte while 
          reaching for a napkin. What started as an embarrassing moment turned into hours of 
          conversation and laughter.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 italic">
          "Sometimes the best things happen when you least expect them."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-primary-600 mb-4">
          The Proposal
        </h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Three years later, Clark planned a surprise trip back to that same coffee shop. 
          After a beautiful day exploring their favorite spots around the city, he got down 
          on one knee right where they first met. Of course, she said yes!
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 italic">
          "The best decision I ever made was saying yes to coffee that day."
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-200 to-primary-200 rounded-2xl aspect-square flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center p-8">
            <svg class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto text-white mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"></path>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-white text-lg font-semibold">The Proposal</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center bg-primary-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif text-neutral-800 mb-4">
        "Love is not about how many days, months, or years you have been together. 
        Love is about how much you love each other every single day."
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">â€” Unknown</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
